    "authors": "Chandu M",
    "name": "v1.0 - Core Lead Capture System",
    "description": "This workflow automatically captures Instagram direct messages, analyzes user intent using AI, and classifies leads into hot, warm, or cold categories.\n\nHot leads are instantly stored in Google Sheets and trigger real-time email alerts, ensuring you never miss a potential customer. Warm and cold leads are also stored for future follow-ups.\n\nBuilt using n8n and OpenAI, this system helps businesses automate lead qualification, streamline customer communication, and improve response time.\n\nKey Features:\n• AI-powered intent detection\n• Automatic lead scoring (hot/warm/cold)\n• Google Sheets CRM integration\n• Instant email alerts for high-priority leads\n• Scalable and customizable workflow\n\nPerfect for agencies, freelancers, and businesses generating leads through Instagram.",
